Sorry for being out of touch, this should make it simpler to manage

Instead of making you add the files/folders that you WANT to check,
now the check script will exclude files that you don't want to check for
changes .

To add files you don't want to check, just add file/folder names between
the parentheses, like:
```
DO_NOT_CHECK=(
     Readme.md
     "A File With Spaces.txt"
     Junk
)
```
